room_title: Escape room "The Manor" by Hellscream Room Escapes in Colorado Springs
room_address: 3021 N. Hancock Ave, Colorado Springs, CO 80907
room_description:
Dr. VonHellton has invited you to his Manor. A rare invitation indeed. As aspiring scientists, much like the good doctor once was, you are seeking his advice for future research. Only, Dr. VonHellton has taken it upon himself to provide you with his own form of inspiration.
You can choose a non-scary version of the game.
